<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Hakmer 29 Cleric</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-01-24 04:47:30</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Need a full grp in the high twenties to low thirties. He spawns in the TAE throne room. He is blue to me but many others spawn in room are higher. Also can get lizardscale cloak in this room.</font></td></tr></table>
